headline: CMS rejects Humana’s Medicare Advantage star ratings appeal
summary: The decision, which Humana disclosed in a Tuesday filing with the court overseeing its lawsuit against the HHS, will be reviewed by Dr. Mehmet Oz, the new CMS administrator.

headline: New Report from the Humana Foundation Examines Best-Practices in Community-Engaged Research
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., April 16, 2025--The Humana Foundation, the philanthropic arm of Humana Inc. for the past 44 years, today announced the publication of its new report, Strengthening Science and Community Impact Through Equitable Research Practices. The report examines innovative research methods adopted by the Foundation’s partners to promote health equity in public health research through community-engaged research practices.
